<br>
I port myself up to luclin everyday and check all the merchants in shadowhaven for decent loot, since almost everything from luclin is sold for less then 10pp on merchants. <br>
<br>
For exemple, my enchanter managed to earn 10k this way, and if you look for good gear in ec/gfay/fp that is cheap while you sell the stuff you found for about 10% the normal price (in his case: spider fur stuff, froglok crown, incandent gloves, ring of frost spider, giant scalemail leggings, black crystal robe, nobles staff and more) you can get nice gear too. My new pally on rallos has a 20/30 weapon already (yeah, centis are cheap, but great ratios) and I got my rogue a 10/22 piercer for 8pp.<br>
<br>
EDIT: didn´t see the post above me, which is about the same way I do it (I did some other stuff while posting this, so it took me a while <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upriae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Priae</A> at: 3/7/02 12:50:12 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uazzimmov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Azzimmov</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/02 1:43:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10167.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> erm...</span><hr size=1> You know that most monks view MQ'ing our epic pieces the way you guys view twinks on this board.Please don't offer that solution to people looking to make money.Enough people do it as is.<br>
<br>
<br>
.....and it's irritating <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upaldor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Paldor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/02 2:18:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10167.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: erm...</span><hr size=1> You want money?<br>
<br>
Don't ever "Give" anything.<br>
<br>
